prediction.sparql:
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT ?senator ?start ?end WHERE {
  VALUES ?senator {
    wd:Q453893 wd:Q359888
  }
  .
  ?senator p:P39 ?positionStatement .
  ?positionStatement ps:P39 wd:Q4416090 ; pq:P580 ?start ; pq:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= '2013-12-31T00:00:00Z' ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?end >= '2013-01-01T00:00:00Z' ^^ xsd:dateTime ) .
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?actor WHERE {
  wd:Q3577037 wdt:P161 ?actor .
  ?actor wdt:P453 ?role .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?role ) , 'donna' ) )
}

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT ?coach WHERE {
  wd:Q330120 p:P286 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P286 ?coach .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?startTime .
  ?statement pq:P582 ?endTime .
  FILTER ( ?startTime <= '2013-01-01' ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?endTime >= '2013-12-31' ^^ xsd:dateTime )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/>
SELECT ?place ?placeLabel ?description WHERE {
  ?place wdt:P131 wd:Q16556 .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?place rdfs:label ?placeLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?placeLabel ) = "en" )
  }
  ?place schema:description ?description .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?description ) = "en" )
}
LIMIT 10
